{"title":"炉前迎新辞旧","authors":["王恩宇"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":12,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉前迎新辞旧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王恩宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的一年要和咱炉工告别，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依难舍，话语滔滔不绝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问我们：炉边共度过三百多个日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，还有什么事情要说、赠言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要写？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢走！请带上这除夕的又一个高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产纪录，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去填进你日历的最后一页！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪知一九七九年却欢笑着前来相"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！这张捷报应挂在我的阳春三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们提前两个月跨进新的年度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我早就在等着把这个纪录迎接！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！新的一年兴冲冲向炉边跑来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们挥钎写吧：迈步从头越！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}